text: Radek Zavadil (born 16 March 1973) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. His sister Lenka Zavadilová is also an Olympic rower. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Prague
